metadata.name: Blue Mountain Boy
metadata.description:
The Nostalgia Collection is a collection of retro-style pieces that are an homage to my creative adolescence in some way shape or form. 

Blue Mountain Boy is a nod toward my Jamaican roots as an artist, referencing the Jamaican Blue Mountains. Since those mountains are a natural wonder back in my homeland, I wanted the greenery spread all over his face to symbolize a form of ambiguousness & wonder.
